    "reply_to_intents": [],
    "weight": 1.0
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "key": "EV_FE_SCI_OF#00020",
    "text": "[CURIOUS] Did you get hit hard during the combat? I want to know before minor problems become major ones.",
